#. js-lingui-id: HP7per
#: src/pages/settings/applications/utils/getStandardApplicationDescription.ts
msgid ""
"The base data model every Twenty workspace runs on.\n"
"\n"
"#### What \"foundation\" means\n"
"\n"
"Every Twenty workspace starts with this set of objects. They define the shape of your CRM, including relationships, activity, and reporting. Everything else, including marketplace apps, AI agents, and custom objects, plugs into them.\n"
"\n"
"#### Included objects\n"
"- **People & Companies**: contact and account records\n"
"- **Opportunities**: your sales pipeline\n"
"- **Notes & Tasks**: activity and follow-ups\n"
"- **Workflows & Dashboards**: automation and reporting\n"
"\n"
"Remove this app and the rest of Twenty has nothing to hang off.\n"
"\n"
"#### Build your own app\n"
"\n"
"Extend Twenty with your own objects, fields, logic functions, or AI skills. Scaffold a new app in one command:\n"
"\n"
"```bash\n"
"npx create-twenty-app@latest my-twenty-app\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"Then inside the folder:\n"
"\n"
"```bash\n"
"cd my-twenty-app\n"
"yarn twenty dev\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"See the [Getting Started guide](https://twenty.com/developers/extend/apps/getting-started) for the full walkthrough, and [Building Apps](https://twenty.com/developers/extend/apps/building) for the `defineApplication` / `defineEntity` APIs."
msgstr ""
"El model de dades base sobre el qual funciona cada espai de treball de Twenty.\n"
"\n"
"#### Què vol dir \"fonament\"\n"
"\n"
"Cada espai de treball de Twenty comença amb aquest conjunt d'objectes. Defineixen l'estructura del teu CRM, incloses les relacions, l'activitat i els informes. La resta, incloses les aplicacions del marketplace, els agents d'IA i els objectes personalitzats, s'hi connecta.\n"
"\n"
"#### Objectes inclosos\n"
"- **Persones i empreses**: registres de contactes i comptes\n"
"- **Oportunitats**: el teu pipeline de vendes\n"
"- **Notes i tasques**: activitat i seguiments\n"
"- **Fluxos de treball i quadres de comandament**: automatització i informes\n"
"\n"
"Si elimines aquesta aplicació, la resta de Twenty es quedarà sense base.\n"
"\n"
"#### Crea la teva pròpia aplicació\n"
"\n"
"Amplia Twenty amb els teus propis objectes, camps, funcions de lògica o habilitats d'IA. Genera l'esquelet d'una aplicació nova amb una sola ordre:\n"
"\n"
"```bash\n"
"npx create-twenty-app@latest my-twenty-app\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"A continuació, dins de la carpeta:\n"
"\n"
"```bash\n"
"cd my-twenty-app\n"
"yarn twenty dev\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"Consulta la [Guia d'inici](https://twenty.com/developers/extend/apps/getting-started) per a la guia completa pas a pas, i [Creació d'aplicacions](https://twenty.com/developers/extend/apps/building) per a les API `defineApplication` / `defineEntity`."

